name: Indonesia in Canada
text: Inclusivity in ASEAN Outlook on Indo – Pacific should be understood as a spirit to find synergy with the existing concepts and working based on communalities out of differences.

name: Indonesia in Canada
text: Inclusivity is a key component in the Indo-Pacific Outlook. It is not intended to isolate any particular country. Not only does it involve major powers in the region, but also engage smaller countries.

name: Indonesia in Canada
text: ASEAN Centrality is necessary as any regional architecture in Indo – Pacific would find it difficult to succeed without a more active role of ASEAN.

name: Indonesia in Canada
text: ASEAN Outlook on Indo Pacific offers a security architecture ensuring that Indian and Pacific oceans are not becoming a site of battle for natural resources, regional conflicts and maritime supremacy.

name: Indonesia in Canada
text: ASEAN Outlook on Indo Pacific is a unified vision of ASEAN Countries which provides us guidance to engage countries and major powers in the region through ASEAN-led mechanism.
